BBEX3.A.HNL.EUR.CA.AB.A04: Exchange rates (comparable rates) for the euro in Honduras * / EUR 1 = HNL ... (selling)
Source: Since March 2003: Banco Central de Honduras, Tegucigalpa 1999 - February 2003: Dresdner Bank Lateinamerika AG, Hamburg.

Methodology: * We do not have any data from Honduras on euro exchange rates; the comparable rates were calculated on the basis of month-end exchange rates for the US dollar in Honduras in conjunction with the respective euro reference exchange rate of the European Central Bank for the US dollar.
